data.description: Step into the embrace of this stunning home, where comfort meets elegance in every corner. As you enter the grand 2-story foyer, a sense of belonging washes over you, a feeling that says, welcome home. This 3-bedroom, 4-bathroom haven is designed for gatherings, offering a spacious open-concept kitchen and living area adorned by a charming fireplace, perfect for cozy moments with loved ones. Gleaming hardwood floors adorn the main living space, adding a touch of sophistication. The separate dining room, complete with a tray ceiling, sets the stage for intimate meals or grand celebrations. Built in 2019, this home is move-in ready, inviting you to make it yours effortlessly. The main floor boasts a primary bedroom retreat with an en suite and a generously sized walk-in closet, offering a private sanctuary. Ascend upstairs to discover a delightful loft, a bathroom, and an ample-sized bedroom with its own walk-in closet#x2014;ideal for guests seeking privacy. But the wonders don't stop there. Descend to the lower level to find a spacious recreation room, a versatile space brimming with possibilities. Complete with a kitchenette for seamless entertaining and a full bath, this area is designed for leisure and social gatherings. Abundant storage in the lower level ensures ample space for all your belongings. And then there's the outdoor charm#x2014;an upper deck and lower stamped concrete patio beckon you to relax, whether it's the tranquil mornings with coffee or the serene evenings with a cocktail, soaking in the peaceful ambiance. As an added bonus, this home comes with thoughtful inclusions: washer, dryer, both refrigerators, a treadmill, and even a magnificent 12-foot Christmas tree#x2014;an embodiment of warmth and holiday cheer. Come and make this inviting space your own, where every detail has been curated to create a life of comfort, style, and joy.
